entries.title: Rep. Knodl to run for state Senate seat
entries.description: (The Center Square) – The race for Wisconsin’s newly open 8th District Senate seat is coming into focus.

entries.title: WV’s COVID-19 state of emergency will end Jan. 1
entries.description: (The Center Square) – West Virginia has been in a state of emergency related to the COVID-19 pandemic for nearly three years, but Gov. Jim Justice announced it ends Jan. 1.
